### Create Package for Review Testing
# @name createPackage
POST {{baseUrl}}/packages/create
Authorization: Bearer {{senderToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "senderEmail": "sender@example.com",
  "receiverName": "Review Receiver",
  "receiverEmail": "review@example.com",
  "receiverPhone": "+1234567896",
  "receiverAddress": "Review Address",
  "receiverCity": "Review City",
  "receiverState": "RC",
  "receiverCountry": "USA",
  "description": "Package for review testing",
  "weight": 1.0,
  "priority": "STANDARD"
}

### Create Review for Package (Sender Only - After Delivery)
POST {{baseUrl}}/reviews/{{packageId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{senderToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Excellent service! Package delivered on time and in perfect condition.",
  "serviceRating": 5,
  "deliverySpeed": 5,
  "courierRating": 5
}

### Get Public Reviews
GET {{baseUrl}}/reviews?page=1&limit=10

### Get Reviews for Specific Package
GET {{baseUrl}}/reviews/package/{{packageId}}